    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329670/extras/c2bac540125a118392c7e9823e7806fb.avif?t=1714113944\" width=617 height=97 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329670/extras/e6c297fda0f881ce4f633c3b61890ea7.avif?t=1714113944\" width=617 height=70 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329670/extras/91df44d6a58aa94cde669a82301cabf6.poster.avif?t=1714113944\" width=600 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329670/extras/91df44d6a58aa94cde669a82301cabf6.webm?t=1714113944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329670/extras/91df44d6a58aa94cde669a82301cabf6.mp4?t=1714113944\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Take good care of your people, provide enough food, trade with your allies and wage wars against your enemies and definitely don't mess with the Greek gods!!<br><br>Lay the foundations for the first democracy, listen to your people and help them with their groundbreaking inventions.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329670/extras/8701c063972b71fe04e40d2bb5038575.avif?t=1714113944\" width=617 height=70 /></span> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329670/extras/e1aa53e0f12819dfe0c6f3ef3145ee9b.poster.avif?t=1714113944\" width=600 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329670/extras/e1aa53e0f12819dfe0c6f3ef3145ee9b.webm?t=1714113944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329670/extras/e1aa53e0f12819dfe0c6f3ef3145ee9b.mp4?t=1714113944\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Build your city for the &quot;normal&quot; population, for the aristocrats and the intellectuals. Make sure that everyone has a job and everyone has a roof over their heads, otherwise a lot of trouble will quickly arise!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329670/extras/9acd962c5660bea47d4cd478989c9572.avif?t=1714113944\" width=617 height=70 /></span> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329670/extras/b1d6cc0ef3bfdba49f228dd53370549e.poster.avif?t=1714113944\" width=600 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329670/extras/b1d6cc0ef3bfdba49f228dd53370549e.webm?t=1714113944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329670/extras/b1d6cc0ef3bfdba49f228dd53370549e.mp4?t=1714113944\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Immerse yourself in ancient Greece. Organize plays that represent current issues in society<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329670/extras/baf10bb527c23af0db54605d89d40e4b.avif?t=1714113944\" width=617 height=70 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329670/extras/7acfa8141d1371ed65bb7c9eefb51d3e.avif?t=1714113944\" width=616 height=166 /></span><br>If there's one thing for sure, it's that you should always be good with the gods! Or bad will happen...<br>If you mess up with the gods, they will send some meteorites, bad thunderstormes or worse....<br>They'll also let you know, if they like you.<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329670/extras/3684e92c90c126dc1fa011009f4a9d37.avif?t=1714113944\" width=617 height=70 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329670/extras/3758781688020d7d55432067602b4996.avif?t=1714113944\" width=616 height=200 /></span><br>Science is one of the most important things in ancient Greek. You need to guide your inhabitants! Give them the possibility to move the earth. Be the best in science.<br><br> <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329670/extras/e4ae1723824b93805314b584e395ad3a.avif?t=1714113944\" width=617 height=70 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329670/extras/467b77718e09e8e9d8a812a67e5efebb.poster.avif?t=1714113944\" width=800 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329670/extras/467b77718e09e8e9d8a812a67e5efebb.webm?t=1714113944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329670/extras/467b77718e09e8e9d8a812a67e5efebb.mp4?t=1714113944\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>If you don't have enough resources, there are 2 ways to get them.  Either you plunder and rob other polis or you start trade partnerships with allies. Which one you choose is up to you!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329670/extras/78b83b61e1415c3d43e6cd833c72915d.avif?t=1714113944\" width=617 height=70 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329670/extras/3adbb626b1b34d6577f99dc8892e8d11.poster.avif?t=1714113944\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329670/extras/3adbb626b1b34d6577f99dc8892e8d11.webm?t=1714113944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329670/extras/3adbb626b1b34d6577f99dc8892e8d11.mp4?t=1714113944\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>They may look peaceful and huggable, but they are very dangerous! You have to protect your residents from the dangerous wild animals!!<br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>",
